venue.address_1: 380 Chief Justice Cushing Highway, Cohasset, MA
venue.name: Whitney And Thayer Woods - parking area near route 3A

item.description:
We have found a great place to take our pets. This hidden gem is sure to become a favorite of the group. Thanks to Kate for suggesting it and for leading these walks!

This weekend we return to Whitney and Thayer. The weather promises to be nice and Kate has agreed to lead another hike.

Please plan for about 2 hours in the woods. Bring water and snacks for you and your pets please.

Any questions feel free to email me.
item.how_to_find_us: Kate will be driving a Blue Jeep Cherokee
item.name: Return to Whitney and Thayer
